{% set notes %}
{% spaceless %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>The Table Basic component is designed to work with both Twig and vanilla HTML (Twig is the recommended method).</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Refer to the <a href="{{ link['components-table-basic-top-side-headers'] }}" class="e-bolt-text-link">Table Basic with Top and Side Headers</a> page for information on adding the headers.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>Twig:</strong> Use the <code>borderless</code> boolean prop to remove the inner table border (this does not include side headers).</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>HTML:</strong> Add a <code>c-bolt-table-basic--borderless</code> class to the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> to remove the inner table border (this does not include side headers).</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endspaceless %}
{% endset %}

